snippet.title: This Village of Maharashtra Becomes First Cashless Village of India

localized.description:
This is village of Maharashtra becomes the first cashless village of India. Amid demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes, Thane's Dhasai to become India's first cashless village.
